1.7
log
@sync docs to agree on section header (.Sh) order for man pages. This also
matches order used by NetBSD, though we don't use all their sections.

Order is:

NAME
SYNOPSIS
DESCRIPTION
RETURN VALUES
ENVIRONMENT
FILES
EXAMPLES
DIAGNOSTICS
ERRORS
SEE ALSO
STANDARDS
HISTORY
AUTHORS
CAVEATS
BUGS

ok krw@@ millert@@
